    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary F22C1 inline-four, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,200 RPM redline. The longitudinal front-mid engine layout provides a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a Torsen limited-slip differential and a surgical close-ratio 6-speed manual gearbox. All original VIN tags are intact across the factory body panels. The double-wishbone suspension and chassis rigidity remain as sharp as the day it left the assembly line, with zero mechanical lash or bushing fatigue. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically pristine, analog masterpiece.",
      "price": 46500.0,
