    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with factory-tight gaps. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history at authorized dealerships, using exclusively OEM parts. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or environmental exposure. Included with the sale are all original keys, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit breathable car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, collector-grade vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 48900.0,
